143
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,320
She doesn't come here often.

144
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,240
Ms. You, he is looking for Ms. Dai.

145
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,520
Are you Mr. Peng?

146
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,720
Yes, I am.

147
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,200
I know that

148
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,880
I hurt Xiaoyu a lot.

149
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,280
I also tried my best

150
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,560
to apologize to her sincerely.

151
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,880
It's not about an apology.

152
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,960
You stabbed her and drained her blood.

153
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,320
Do you think apologies work?

154
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:39,440
Even if you stitch the wound,

155
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,960
