160
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,920
I came back

161
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,960
to Shanghai

162
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,280
to get a divorce.

163
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,080
