164
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,160
You only think about the divorce now.

165
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,880
Isn't it a bit late?

166
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:00,800
You shouldn't screw around if you're still married.

167
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,120
I didn't screw around with her.

168
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,520
I really am in love with Xiaoyu.

169
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,280
Mr. Peng,

170
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:12,160
I don't think you know what love is.

171
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,800
You know

172
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:15,640
that Xiaoyu is willful.

173
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,920
I've been patient and tolerant.

174
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:17,680
I know that I...

175
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:18,860
But patience and tolerance

176
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:20,760
are included in love by default.

177
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:23,320
For example, if my chef

178
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,400
tells me

179
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,240
"Oh look, boss,

180
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,600
I can cook this raw food",

181
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:28,440
