182
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,240
Here's my advice.

183
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,040
Don't come to Xiaoyu again.

184
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:46,760
I...

185
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,080
I will not give Xiaoyu up.

186
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,320
That's not for you to decide.

187
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,640
Who are you to say that?

188
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:53,600
I am her friend.

189
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,600
As long as I'm here,

190
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,800
